# Cursor Rules for Voddly Project

## NEVER EDIT THESE FILES

- `app/src/lib/encore-client.ts` - This is auto-generated by Encore. Any changes will be overwritten.
- `encore-client.ts` (any location) - Auto-generated Encore client files should never be manually edited.

## Project Structure

- Backend code goes in `/backend` directory
- Frontend code goes in `/app` directory
- Use pnpm for all package management commands
- Never create README files automatically

## Code Style

- Use arrow functions consistently
- Prefer absolute paths over relative paths for tool calls
- Always check linter errors before completing tasks

## Database Access

- Frontend hooks can query SQLite database directly when needed
- Prefer local database queries over backend API calls for metadata enhancement
